label: Appeal from Orangeburg County, The State against Cleveland Louis Sellers, Jr., Volume IV
description: Legal document entitled, "In the State of South Carolina In The Supreme Court, Appeal From Orangeburg County, Honorable John Grimball, Presiding Judge, The State, Respondent, against Cleveland Louis Sellers, Jr., Appellant, Transcript of Record."
